ygData.subject: Re: [EverQuest] Powerleveling Guide
ygData.msgSnippet: ... i will not comment, how good or bad those guides are, but: this link can be considered a warez link, because those documents are copyrighted material
ygData.messageBody:
On 7 Oct 2002 at 21:13, freeeqguides wrote:

> Get your free copy of Padrino's Power Levelling Guide at
> http://www.freewebs.com/freeeqguides/index.htm

i will not comment, how good or bad those "guides" are, but:

this link can be considered a "warez" link, because those documents
are copyrighted material and sold for money.

even if the purpose of the provider can be considered "good for the eq community", it is pretty illegal what
(s)he is doing.

also a program like "eqw" and "showeq" are illegal to use considering
the EULA of the game and these programs are advertised in those
guides.


- bilt

Biltilie Dwimmerlaik
level 54 female gnome magician
